            <title>1.1.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Dark mode support: all UI elements automatically adapt to the system appearance setting</li>
</ul>
<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Shortcut display now uses symbols (⌃ ⌥ ⇧ ⌘ ← → ↑ ↓) instead of English key names for modifier and arrow keys</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
